Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Sui.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.14,0:02:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Biki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:45.51,EP Title BG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,0)\p1\blur1}m 0 0 l 950 0 950 100 0 100
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.59,0:02:45.51,EP Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1300,0)\be1}The Light of the Eyelids
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.13,0:02:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your eyes still hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.01,0:02:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Biki...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.79,0:02:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you in on a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:03:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I know... what's causing my disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a mushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,living in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,inside my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sui is the youngest daughter of the head family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.58,0:03:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}About a half a year ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}she contracted a disease which\N made her eyes sensitive to light.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}None of the eye doctors could find the cause of her strange illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and before they could even \Nfigure out a course of treatment,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}her eyes became so sensitive that even \Na little light began to cause her great pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.21,0:03:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a result, she was left with our family since we have a sturdy storage shed which blocks out light.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Although it may have been for Sui's own good,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.91,0:04:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1390)}{\i1}it appeared to me that she was abandoned at our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's another eyelid behind my eyelid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a place where outside light can never get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where the mushi live.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.82,0:04:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A second eyelid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know how to close your second eyelid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll teach you how.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.18,0:04:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.18,0:04:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.77,0:04:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I do see some flickering movements within my eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.57,0:04:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after you close your eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,your eyes are still looking at the backs of your eyelids...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,so they're not really closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why, whenever I want it pitch-black,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I close my eyes again to those flickering movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1560)}That's when a curtain of true darkness falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so uncoordinated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:06:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We play in the deep darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.93,0:06:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Although I can't see anything \Nwhen I first step into the shed,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}after a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.19,0:06:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} the outlines of things start to gradually appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.55,0:06:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you see the ball when it's pitch black?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.23,0:06:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because there is a river of light\N running under the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see it if you close your second eyelid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.97,0:06:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,When I keep staring at true darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...from a far, tiny specks of light start appearing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...and they rapidly form into a river.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.21,0:06:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,When I look at it carefully,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.99,0:06:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see that it's all made up of tiny mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.23,0:06:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I try to go closer to get a better look...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get any closer to that river.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a man I've never met before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.78,0:07:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A man with one eye is always on the other side of the river saying that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I just look at the river from a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.18,0:07:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...sometimes become uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those things that Sui sees with her eyes closed...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.06,0:07:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}what on earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.70,0:08:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What on earth can they be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.18,0:08:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Biki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You spend way too much time inside the storage shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I disposed of all the used eye bandages by burning them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And I disinfected my hands \Nand all the eating utensils, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no guarantee that you won't get infected, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.06,0:08:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The head family had the same fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.75,0:08:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they abandoned Sui, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.63,0:08:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.31,0:08:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sui is a very good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.69,0:08:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just have to deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:09:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep supporting her so that she doesn't lose the light in her heart as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1820)}But please...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,don't get infected with that disease like she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.08,0:09:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.21,0:09:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...coming here for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.91,0:10:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.39,0:10:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be... Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:10:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Biki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:10:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Biki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.83,0:11:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Biki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Biki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Biki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...won't be allowed to come here any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He's caught your illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.05,0:11:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not... your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our fault for taking pity on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there? If you leave \Nthe storm door open, Biki will!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.89,0:12:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I am an expert in these matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.67,0:12:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I applied medicine and some painkiller.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.09,0:12:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaving him in the dark will only make the disease progress further.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Ginko. I am a mushi-shi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I caught wind of the girl in your storage shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.59,0:12:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Her disease is something that can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.72,0:12:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...cured by an eye doctor, but by a mushi-shi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:13:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Will Biki... will my son be cured?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.75,0:13:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the mushi he has seems to be a newborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So treatment with medicine alone\N will probably be effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Biki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.84,0:13:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Biki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Biki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.09,0:13:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sui!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you're awake now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your eyes still hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. The medicine worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The cause of Sui's illness is the {\i1}Manako-Yami{\i0} mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs42\bord2.5\fad(50,50)\pos(640,30.667)}{\i1}Note:- Manako = eye, Yami = darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They multiply in darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You spent too much time with Sui in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.09,0:14:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You know Sui?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.76,0:14:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's one-eyed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.00,0:14:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time I closed my second eyelid,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,she was on the opposite bank of the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.26,0:14:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.73,0:14:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That river of light is comprised of \Na different element from earthly light.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.03,0:14:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's harmful to your eyes if you look at it too closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.37,0:14:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He has his other eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if he's a different person\N from the one Sui mentioned...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll start Sui's treatment after the sun sets.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.13,0:14:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sui!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.09,0:15:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.71,0:15:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,After I told you so many times not to go into the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sui...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:16:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sui's eyeballs are already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.97,0:16:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll try something anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.39,0:16:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If you close your second eyelid for too long, your eyeball gets eaten by the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, ready, Sui?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to lure out the mushi with the moonlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.14,0:16:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,While keeping your second eyelid closed,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.70,0:16:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly open your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out, mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There's light out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,M-mushi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sui, that's enough. Close your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:17:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... let's take a look at Sui's eyeballs...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.32,0:18:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,M-mushi! There really was a mushi in Sui's eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought, her eyes are no longer functioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.09,0:18:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if this will work, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.52,0:18:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give this to Sui.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you've been overreacting for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't freak out so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.82,0:18:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a glass eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the liquid mushi that you saw earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.79,0:18:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If I inject this into a glass ball, it should turn into a functioning eyeball.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.83,0:18:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.93,0:18:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That river of light that you both can see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.24,0:18:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what is it anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.79,0:19:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Try closing your second eyelid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.02,0:19:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then the path to darkness will be revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.59,0:19:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Long ago, you too were watching it, just like us...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.53,0:19:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From the time a person opens his eyes to the light,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.43,0:19:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he is said to have forgotten \Nhow to close his second eyelid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, it was perhaps for the better to those living,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}for before that time, it is said that\N many had lost their eyesight...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}from staring too much at the river of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.18,0:20:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The second eyelid, true darkness, alien light...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.47,0:20:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The group of infinite life forms\N swimming beneath our feet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All around us became really bright and right after, we were plunged into darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.11,0:20:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the ground fell out beneath me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.82,0:20:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and I saw a river of light flowing way below.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.22,0:20:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It just happened for a split second after that mushi-shi-san put the glass eye into you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.77,0:20:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was so pretty and I felt as though my body was being pulled into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.05,0:20:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to stare at it forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.60,0:20:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.46,0:21:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sui came out of the shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She looks a lot at the trees and flowers and light.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.97,0:21:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She will probably never be lured by that strange light in the darkness again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.86,0:21:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if that mushi-shi lost \Nhis real eye in the same way Sui did...
